var e=JSON.parse(`[{"id":"L2_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MINISTER_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"아! 왔군. 마리아 안토노프 중장. 막 리허설이 시작되려던 참일세.","JPN":"あ！来たか、マリア・アントノフ中将。たった今、リハーサルが始まったところだ。","ENG":"Ah! So you've come, Lieutenant General Maria Antonov. The rehearsal is just about to begin.","TWN":"啊！妳來了啊，瑪麗亞·安東諾夫中將。彩排正好要開始了。"},"stage":{"bg":"AB_UI_NKM_UI_CUTSCEN_BG_MAINSTREAM_001010","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L3_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MARIA_DELTA_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"반갑습니다, 장관님. 프로젝트의 공개 참관을 허락해주셔서 고맙군요.","JPN":"お会いできて光栄です、長官。プロジェクトの公開演習をご承諾いただき、ありがとうございます。","ENG":"Very nice to see you, Mr. Secretary. Thank you for allowing me to sit in on the open viewing of the project.","TWN":"見到您很高興，長官。謝謝您允許我參觀這個計畫。"},"stage":{"bg":"AB_UI_NKM_UI_CUTSCEN_BG_MAINSTREAM_001010","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"MARIA_DELTA_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L5_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MINISTER_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"당연한 걸 고마워하지 말게. 오히려 소파에 앉아 TV로 편하게 봐도 됐을 텐데 말이야.","JPN":"当然のことだからお礼は結構だ。むしろソファーに座ってテレビで見てるほうが楽だったと思うがな。","ENG":"No need to thank me for doing what should be done. If anything, you could've just watched from the comfort of your own television back home.","TWN":"不用謝，這是我應該做的。反倒是中將，明明妳可以舒服地坐在沙發上用電視觀看的。"},"stage":{"bg":"AB_UI_NKM_UI_CUTSCEN_BG_MAINSTREAM_001010","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"MARIA_DELTA_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L6_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MARIA_DELTA_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"그런데, 시연 방식이 조금 독특하더군요.","JPN":"ところで、演習の方法が少し独特ですね。","ENG":"By the way, the demonstration methodology seemed rather unusual.","TWN":"不過，這個表演方式似乎有些獨特呢。"},"stage":{"bg":"AB_UI_NKM_UI_CUTSCEN_BG_MAINSTREAM_001010","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"MARIA_DELTA_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L7_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MARIA_DELTA_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"특공부대원들과 10대 1 근접전투라니. 이런 게 정말로 의미가 있는 시연입니까?","JPN":"特攻部隊員たちと10対1の近接戦闘とは。これは本当に有意味な試演なのでしょうか？","ENG":"A 10-on-1 melee with special forces troops? Does this sort of thing really bear much meaning in this demonstration?","TWN":"居然與特種部隊隊員進行10對1的近身格鬥。這種表演真的有意義嗎？"},"stage":{"bg":"AB_UI_NKM_UI_CUTSCEN_BG_MAINSTREAM_001010","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"MARIA_DELTA_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L9_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MINISTER_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"하하, 공개 프로젝트인 만큼 모든 매스컴의 주목을 받고 있으니 말이지.","JPN":"はは、公開プロジェクトということもあって、全マスコミから注目されているからな。","ENG":"Hah hah, given that it's a public project, we've got the attention of all the media.","TWN":"哈哈，既然這是公開的計畫，就一定要足夠吸引媒體的眼球啊。"},"stage":{"bg":"AB_UI_NKM_UI_CUTSCEN_BG_MAINSTREAM_001010","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"MARIA_DELTA_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L10_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MINISTER_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"이 프로젝트의 중요성을 과시하기에 대련만큼 직관적인 수단도 없다네.","JPN":"このプロジェクトの重要性を見せつけるのに、立ち合い稽古ほど効果的なものもない。","ENG":"There's nothing as effective as sparring to demonstrate the importance of this project.","TWN":"要展現這個計畫重要性，對練就是最直觀的手段了。"},"stage":{"bg":"AB_UI_NKM_UI_CUTSCEN_BG_MAINSTREAM_001010","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"MARIA_DELTA_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L11_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MINISTER_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"우리가 실질적으로 추진하는 프로젝트는 유능한 군인을 키워내는 일이지만......","JPN":"我々が実際に推進しているプロジェクトは、有能な軍人を育てることだが……","ENG":"Although what we're really after is to foster capable service members...","TWN":"雖然我們的計畫實質上是培養優秀的軍人……"},"stage":{"bg":"AB_UI_NKM_UI_CUTSCEN_BG_MAINSTREAM_001010","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"MARIA_DELTA_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L12_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MINISTER_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"그런 내용을 단상 위에서 실컷 떠들어봤자 국민의 지지를 받긴 힘들거든.","JPN":"そんな内容を壇上に立って喋っても、国民の支持を得られにくいからな。","ENG":"We can't win the support of the public on that talking point, no matter how long we spend giving a speech on the pedestal.","TWN":"但不管再怎麼吹噓這個計畫有多重要，大概也很難得到國民的支持。"},"stage":{"bg":"AB_UI_NKM_UI_CUTSCEN_BG_MAINSTREAM_001010","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"MARIA_DELTA_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L13_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MINISTER_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"프로젝트의 주인공이 수적 불리의 상황을 멋지게 극복해내는 연출만큼 정치적 편파를 떠나 만인의 지지를 받기 좋은 장치도 없지.","JPN":"プロジェクトの主人公が、数の上での不利な状況を見事に乗り越える演出こそ、\\n政治的偏見によらず万人の支持を得るのにちょうどいい措置だ。","ENG":"An outnumbered protagonist overcoming his struggle... There's no method more effective than this plot device, regardless of the political leanings of the audience.","TWN":"像電影主角那樣帥氣克服各種難關，以一己之力打敗數量眾多的敵人……要讓人們拋開政治偏見支持我們，這是最好的方法了。"},"stage":{"bg":"AB_UI_NKM_UI_CUTSCEN_BG_MAINSTREAM_001010","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"MARIA_DELTA_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L17_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MARIA_DELTA_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"잘 차려 입은 저 친구가 프로젝트의 주인공입니까?","JPN":"ドレスアップした彼がプロジェクトの主人公ですか？","ENG":"So is that sharply dressed fellow the protagonist of the project?","TWN":"那位衣冠楚楚的朋友就是這個計畫的主角嗎？"},"stage":{"bg":"AB_UI_NKM_UI_CUTSCEN_BG_MAINSTREAM_001010","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":{"char_id":"MARIA_DELTA_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"}}}},{"id":"L19_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MINISTER_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"그렇다네. 이름은 카일 웡. 이번 프로젝트의 대표주자라고 할 수 있는 최고 엘리트 훈련병이지.","JPN":"そうだ。彼の名前はカイル・ウォン。今回のプロジェクトのメインメンバーとも言える超エリート訓練兵だ。","ENG":"That's right. His name is Kyle Wong. He's an elite trainee. We could virtually dub him as the best of the best in this project.","TWN":"沒錯。他叫凱爾。他可以說是這次計畫的主力，是非常優秀的精英訓練兵。"},"stage":{"bg":"AB_UI_NKM_UI_CUTSCEN_BG_MAINSTREAM_001010","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":{"char_id":"MARIA_DELTA_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"}}}},{"id":"L20_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MINISTER_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"적당한 사복이면 괜찮다고 했는데, 자네가 참관할 거라 귀띔했더니 기어이 저 복장을 고르더군.","JPN":"普段通りの私服で構わないと言ってたが、君が参観することを耳打ちしてやったら、あの服を纏ったわけだ。","ENG":"I told him he's free to wear anything, but he insisted on wearing that when I let him know you'd be watching.","TWN":"雖然我說穿合適的衣服就行，但他聽說你會參觀，所以選了那套服裝。"},"stage":{"bg":"AB_UI_NKM_UI_CUTSCEN_BG_MAINSTREAM_001010","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":{"char_id":"MARIA_DELTA_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"}}}},{"id":"L22_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MARIA_DELTA_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"음? 저 친구가 저를 알고 있답니까?","JPN":"うん？　彼が私のことを知っていたんですか？","ENG":"Huh? He knows about me?","TWN":"嗯？那位朋友認識我嗎？"},"stage":{"bg":"AB_UI_NKM_UI_CUTSCEN_BG_MAINSTREAM_001010","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"MARIA_DELTA_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_SURPRISE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L24_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MINISTER_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"겸손하긴. 자넨 전쟁에서 인류를 승리로 이끈 영웅이지 않나.","JPN":"そんなに謙遜することはない。君は戦争で人類を勝利に導いた英雄じゃないか。","ENG":"No need to be so modest. You led humanity to victory in the last war. You're a hero.","TWN":"太謙虛了。妳可是帶領人類走向勝利的英雄啊。"},"stage":{"bg":"AB_UI_NKM_UI_CUTSCEN_BG_MAINSTREAM_001010","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"MARIA_DELTA_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L25_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MINISTER_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"난 물론이고, 자넬 밀어내고 싶어하는 보수파 의원들조차, 자네의 업적만큼은 존중할 수 밖에 없다네.","JPN":"私はもちろん、君を落としたがる保守派の議員たちですら、君の功績だけは高く評価している。","ENG":"Even my conservative opponents who'd rather see you gone have no choice but to acknowledge your accomplishments.","TWN":"別說我了，就連那些想趕走你的保守派議員，也都很尊敬妳的成就。"},"stage":{"bg":"AB_UI_NKM_UI_CUTSCEN_BG_MAINSTREAM_001010","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"MARIA_DELTA_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L26_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MINISTER_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"저 친구는 특히 더 그렇지.","JPN":"彼の場合は言うまでもない。","ENG":"It's even more the case with that fellow.","TWN":"那位朋友尤其如此。"},"stage":{"bg":"AB_UI_NKM_UI_CUTSCEN_BG_MAINSTREAM_001010","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"MARIA_DELTA_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L27_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MINISTER_NPC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"평소에도 열심히 했지만, 자네가 훈련소를 방문하는 날이면 유독 기합이 잔뜩 들어가곤 했거든.","JPN":"普段も頑張っているが、君が訓練場を訪問する日はなおさら気合が入ってたんだ。","ENG":"Although he was always hard working, he'd grow extra enthusiastic on the days you visited the training camp.","TWN":"雖然他平時就很認真，但妳訪問訓練所的日子他格外賣力。"},"stage":{"bg":"AB_UI_NKM_UI_CUTSCEN_BG_MAINSTREAM_001010","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"MARIA_DELTA_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}}]`);export{e as default};